          <p class="ba-sub">For local businesses that need high-quality, manually verified citations built across top directories.</p>
        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Whitespark specializes in citation building — finding, building, and tracking the directory listings that support Google Maps rankings. The Citation Finder identifies which citations your competitors have that you don't. Manual submission ensures accuracy at each directory rather than bulk API submissions. The geo-grid rank tracker shows Maps position across a geographic grid. Whitespark covers the citation-building side of listing management that automated sync tools like Moz Local and Yext handle differently.</p>
