        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Synup provides automated listing distribution to 60+ directories with near-real-time sync and duplicate suppression. The price point at $34.99/month sits between Moz Local ($20/month) and Yext ($499/year) and covers more directories than Moz Local without the vendor lock-in of Yext. Accuracy monitoring alerts you when third-party edits override your data. Suitable for businesses that find Moz Local's 90-directory coverage insufficient but don't need Yext's 200+ platform reach.</p>
